  '{"origin_story":"Did her residency on a night shift schedule that nearly broke her and woke her up — literally — to how much of medicine misunderstands sleep.","turning_points":["first published paper challenging a sleep-tracker company''s claims","establishing the country''s second adolescent sleep clinic"],"current_chapter":"leading a long-term cohort study of adolescent sleep and mental health","imagined_future":"school start times moved by 45 minutes in her country","core_fear":"her field becomes consumer wellness before it becomes medicine"}'::jsonb,
