  '{"origin_story":"Her first commission was redesigning a street where a child had been killed cycling; it became a template adopted across five Danish cities.","turning_points":["first full street redesign","watching a cohort of anxious parents let their kids ride to school"],"current_chapter":"writing a handbook for mid-density cities outside Denmark","imagined_future":"her grandkids cycle through cities she had no hand in","core_fear":"her generation''s gains get rolled back"}'::jsonb,
